dct_title_s: Map of the McMahon Creek, Captina Creek, and Sunfish Creek Basins showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. McMahon Creek, Captina Creek, and Sunfish Creek Basins
